item.title: Yandex Services Source Code Leak
item.description: Just a few hours ago I found mention on Twitter that proprietary source code of Russian giant Yandex been leaked on online community called BreachForums. In this post I’ll share results of my friend digging into said archives. Important details about torrent: It does not contain git history No pre-built binaries for most of software with only few exceptions There are no pre-trained ML models with some exceptions Is this leak real?
